{"type": "article", "id": 26292, "title": "可以体验漂浮感的水床", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-03T06:50:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 91, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021325056HnivgwfT3lB15DO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">Zerobody 是由 spa 设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.starpool.com/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://www.starpool.com/', 'Starpool');\" target=\"_blank\">Starpool</a> 和脑健康研究公司 <a href=\"http://www.neocogita.com/en/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://www.neocogita.com/en/', 'Neocogita');\" target=\"_blank\">Neocogita</a> 共同推出的一款加热的水床。平躺在上面的时候，能够体会到漂浮的感觉，所以也被称为“干水池”（dry pool）。在“漂浮”的过程中，人体内产生的脑内啡会压抑疼痛信号的传递，使人感到欣快。除此之外，配套的 <a href=\"http://www.nurelax.com/en/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://www.nurelax.com/en/', 'NU RELAX');\" target=\"_blank\">NU RELAX</a> 提供专门为此设计的冥想环节，你可以通过收听音频来让身体彻底放松。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132503aB1HcRsNuqQlLxtJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132503nKZS8lyEWp5udA6j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132504kGDH7e5sY8ATrhEn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132504NkBser7qCf0O82p9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}